data.description: COTTAGE-STYLE HOME in QUIET NEIGHBORHOOD.   This charming home offers 2 BEDROOMS on the MAIN LEVEL and a LARGE LOFT used by sellers as their main bedroom, spanning 38' in length.   Original Shiplap in stairwell ?   UnFinished BASEMENT with LAUNDRY AREA.    DUAL THERMOSTATS.    Detached GARAGE.   ORIGINAL HARDWOOD FLOORS in main rooms.    Wood-burning FIREPLACE.    Linen SHELVES in BATHROOM.     Newer 33' x 29' COVERED BACK DECK over 45' x 33' CONCRETE PAD for storage and/or kid-height play area.    FENCED  BACKYARD with a lot of additional yard behind extending to 1st Ave.    Concrete PARKING PAD in BACK with ELECTRICITY.    Extra asphalt parking off street in front.   Cobra SECURITY SYSTEM.    New owner may desire to touchup or finish some places;  See photos.
